<br>
Focus Items will only function on summons from level 4 to 49, Staffs of Elemental Mastery will function on summons from level 49 to 60 (Not including the Decoy summons). <br>
<br>
Ok, I got my foci at level 1.  I am 100% sure they don't appear larger.  I can't tell any difference in the HP or damage output of the focused pets vs non focused.  Everyone on my server that I've talked to says they don't work until 34.  My magi hit level 12 today and i summoned an even con water pets 3 times out of 4 tries(may be just luck) with the stein focus.  I'm pretty lost on whether or not I should just stick them in the bank for later or keep using them.  The only thing I have noticed is that my pets taunt like a Mo FO(my main is a necro and they seem to taunt better than my lvl 49 necro pet and my magi is only level 12)  Not sure if its just the focused ones that do that or all magi pets.<br>
<br>
Please post any facts or maybe point me to a study that has been done on focused pets.  If you want, give me your opinion on your pre 34 focused pets vs non focused. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/umarthisdil.showPublicProfile?language=EN>marthisdil</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#333333>(3/21/01 2:46:00 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlibrarysubmissions.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=34.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Do focus items work pre 34???</span><hr size=1> The pet Foci do not work until L34 and stop working on pets after L49 (they also do not affect, in any way, Monster Summoning line of spells).<br>
<br>
